Class PMMLConditionTranslator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.knime.base.node.mine.decisiontree2.PMMLConditionTranslator
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    PMMLDecisionTreeTranslator

    public abstract class PMMLConditionTranslator
extends Object
    Condition translator between raw PMML and KNIME's representation.
    Based on the former PMMLDecisionTreeTranslator from wenlin, Zementis Inc., Apr 2011, now, that is a subclass.
    Since:
    2.9
    Author:
    Gabor Bakos
